    "description": "\n<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n    <div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n    <span property=\"description\">Meet your all in one prospecting adventure kit from ASR Outdoor.\n\nDesigned for gold seekers who like to venture into remote terrain. Whether you're an experienced prospector or just getting started, this gold panning kit equips you with the gear you need to find and recover gold, no matter where your journey takes you. Walk or hike to just about any river or creek with essential gold prospecting equipment on your back, where you can immediately start panning for gold, with minimal set up time required. \n\nAll gold prospecting equipment included in this gold panning kit, conveniently fits inside the included ASR Outdoor 30L backpack, so you can remain hands free when you’re on the go, and easily pack everything out when you’re done for the day.\n\nHere’s what’s included: \n\nDurable 30L Backpack: Built tough for the backcountry, this spacious pack carries all your gear comfortably with reinforced seams, padded and adjustable shoulder straps, and multiple compartments\n\nClassifier Screens (Multiple Sizes): Speed up your panning process with lightweight, stackable screens that separate larger rocks and debris from finer material, ideal for high efficiency prospecting\n\nGold Pans: High quality 14 inch single riffle and 12 inch dual riffle gold pans ensure you never miss a flake, whether working in a riverbed or remote stream\n\n8lb Magnetic Pick Up Tool: Remove unwanted magnetic black sand from concentrates quickly, lightweight and perfect for field use\n\n3-in-1 Shovel: Compact yet rugged, this digging tool is ready to tackle any terrain, whether breaking hard ground, scooping gravel or digging into riverbanks\n\nCollapsible Bucket with Stand: Lightweight and portable, this foldable bucket is perfect for collecting water or transporting pay dirt; packs down small to save space.\n\nFine Gold Recovery Tools: Everything you need to help recover and store even the tiniest specs of gold with ease\n\nDesigned for portability and performance, the 14pc Remote Rucksack Gold Panning Kit is your reliable companion for off the grid gold adventures. Whether hiking into remote streams or exploring historic goldfields, you’ll have all the tools needed to pan, classify, recover and store found gold. Good luck!</span>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n    \n    \n        <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n        <style type=\"text/css\">\n            /* FONTS AND COLORS */\n            body {\n                font-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n                font-size: 14px;\n                line-height: 1.428571429;\n                color: #333;\n                background-color: white;\n            }\n            h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n                color: black;\n            }\n            p {\n                white-space: pre-line;\n            }\n            .navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n                color: #333;\n            }\n    \n            .product-specs {\n                background-color: #f1f1f1;\n                padding: 1em;\n            }\n            .product-specs td {\n                font-size:12px;\n            }\n            .attr-left {\n                min-width:6em;\n                font-weight:bold;\n                vertical-align:top;\n            }\n            .attr-right {\n                vertical-align:top;\n            }\n    \n            div.footer {\n                border-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n            }\n    \n            .navbar-default {\n                background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n                background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n                background-repeat: repeat-x;\n                border-radius: 4px;\n                -web