\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">REMOTE GOLD PANNING KIT: Designed for gold seekers who like to venture into remote terrain, this gold panning kit equips you with the essential gold prospecting equipment needed to find and recover gold, no matter where your journey takes you</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">30L RUCKSACK: All the gold prospecting equipment included with this gold panning kit fit into the large capacity backpack, meaning you can hike with all your gold prospecting equipment and personal belongings to just about any remote location</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">CLASSIFIER SCREEN SET: Essential for removing unwanted materials like gravels and rocks from your paydirt to increase gold yield; this set includes three large stacking classifier screens in 1/8 inch, 1/12 and 1/20 inch mesh sizes to be used in conjunction with the collapsible bucket</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">GOLD PANS: This gold panning kit includes one large 14 inch single riffle gold and one standard size 12 inch dual riffle gold pan; the single riffle gold pan allows for the initial panning of a larger sample, while the dual riffle is great to move to for finishing concentrates</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">FINE GOLD RECOVERY TOOLS: Included are a pair of tweezers, an 8lb magnetic pick up tool, 3 in 1 shovel, eye loupe and more to help with the extraction and storage of found gold</td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>ASR Outdoor Remote Adventure 30L Rucksack Gold Panning Kit with Classifier Screens, 14pc (3 Colors)</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">169.99</span></h2>\n                <p>Meet your all in one prospecting adventure kit from ASR Outdoor.\n\nDesigned for gold seekers who like to venture into remote terrain. Whether you're an experienced prospector or just getting started, this gold panning kit equips you with the gear you need to find and recover gold, no matter where your journey takes you. Walk or hike to just about any river or creek with essential gold prospecting equipment on your back, where you can immediately start panning for gold, with minimal set up time required. \n\nAll gold prospecting equipment included in this gold panning kit, conveniently fits inside the included ASR Outdoor 30L backpack, so you can remain hands free when you’re on the go, and easily pack everything out when you’re done for the day.\n\nHere’s what’s included: \n\nDurable 30L Backpack: Built tough for the backcountry, this spacious pack carries all your gear comfortably with reinforced seams, padded and adjustable shoulder straps, and multiple compartments\n\nClassifier Screens (Multiple Sizes): Speed up your panning process with lightweight, stackable screens that separate larger rocks and debris from finer material, ideal for high efficiency prospecting\n\nGold Pans: High quality 14 inch single riffle and 12 inch dual riffle gold pans ensure you never miss a flake, whether working in a riverbed or remote stream\n\n8lb Magnetic Pick Up Tool: Remove unwanted magnetic black sand from concentrates quickly, lightweight and perfect for field use\n\n3-in-1 Shovel: Compact yet rugged, this digging tool is ready to tackle any terrain, whether breaking hard ground, scooping gravel or digging into riverbanks\n\nCollapsible Bucket with Stand: Lightweight and portable, this foldable bucket is perfect for collecting water or transporting pay dirt; packs down small to save space.\n\nFine Gold Recovery Tools: Everything you need to help recover and store even the tiniest specs of gold with ease\n\nDesigned for portability and performance, the 14pc Remote Rucksack Gold Panning Kit is your reliable companion for off the grid gold adventures. Whether hiking into remote streams or exploring historic goldfields, you’ll have all the tools needed to pan, classify, recover and store found gold. Good luck!</p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n                        <p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n                        <a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n                <p>© 2026</p>\n            </div> <!-- /footer -->\n    \n        </div> <!-- /container -->\n        <div style=\"clear:both\">\n            &nbsp;<table></table>\n        </div>\n",
